{
  "chapter": "097",
  "title": "郦生陆贾列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生食其</span>，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈留</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">高阳</span>人。喜欢读书，家境贫穷潦倒，没有<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">衣</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">食</span>谋生的产业，做了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">里监门吏</span>。然而县中的贤豪不敢役使他，县里人都称他为狂生。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈胜</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项梁</span>等起兵时，诸将攻略土地经过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">高阳</span>的有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数十人</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>听说其将领都器量狭小喜好苛细<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼</span>节、自以为是，不能听取大度之言，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>便深深藏起不出。 后来听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>率兵攻略地到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈留</span>郊外，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>麾下有位<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">骑士</span>恰好是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>里中人的儿子，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>常向他询问乡里的贤<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>豪杰。 <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">骑士</span>回家，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>见了他对他说：\"我听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>待人傲慢轻视别人，却有大谋略，这正是我想追随的人，可惜没人给我引荐。你若见到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>，就说'<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>里中有一个<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>，年六十多岁，身高<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">八尺</span>，人都叫他狂生，他自己却说我不是狂生'。\" <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">骑士</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>不喜欢儒生，凡是戴<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">儒冠</span>来的客人，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>往往摘下他的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">冠</span>帽，往里面撒尿。与人谈话，常常大骂。不可以儒生的身份游说。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>说：\"你只管这么说。\" <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">骑士</span>后来从容地按<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>交代的说了。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">高阳</span>的传舍，派人召见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>到了，入内拜见，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>正叉腿坐在床上让两个女子给他洗脚，就这样接见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>进去，作了个长揖，不跪拜，说：\"足下想帮助<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>呢？还是想率领<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>呢？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>骂道：\"竖儒！<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>共同苦于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>已经很久了，所以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>才相继<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，怎么说帮助<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>呢？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>说：\"必须聚集众人召合义兵来<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>无道的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝，不应该傲慢地接见<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长者</span>。\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>停下洗脚，起身整理<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">衣</span>服，请<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>上座，致歉谢罪。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>于是谈论<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">六国从横</span>的事。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>高兴，赐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>吃<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">食</span>，问道：\"计策怎么出？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>说：\"足下率领乌合之众，收拢散乱之兵，不过<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万人</span>，就想径直攻入强大的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，这就像去探<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">虎</span>口。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈留</span>是<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的要冲，四通八达的地方，如今城中又多积<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">粟</span>米。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>与它的县令关系很好，请让我去游说他，让他投降足下。如果不听，足下就发兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>城，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>为内应。\" 于是派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>前去，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>率兵随后，就攻下了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈留</span>。 号<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦食其</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">广野君</span>。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>推荐他的弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦商</span>，让他带<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数千人</span>跟随<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>向<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西南</span>攻略地方。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>常做<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">说客</span>，奔驰出使<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三年</span>秋天，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，攻拔<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>兵逃走据守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">巩</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛水</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>人听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">淮阴侯（韩信）</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>又多次反叛于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>地，就分兵去救援。此时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">淮阴（韩信）</span>正向东<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>多次被困于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">成皋</span>，计划放弃<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">成皋</span>以东，屯兵<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">巩</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛水</span>以抵御<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>于是说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>听说知道天之天的，王业可以成；不知天之天的，王业不可成。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">王者</span>以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>人为天，而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>人以<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">食</span>为天。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">敖仓</span>，是<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>转运粮食的所在已经很久，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>听说它下面储藏的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">粟</span>非常多，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>人攻拔<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>，不坚守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">敖仓</span>，却引兵东去，让谪戍之卒分守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">成皋</span>，这正是上天资助<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>的机会。如今<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>容易攻<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>反而退却，自己放弃有利条件，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>私下以为这是失策。而且两雄不能并立，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>久相对峙而不决胜负，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>骚动，海内摇荡，农夫放下<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">耒</span>耜，工女离开<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">织机</span>，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>之人心未有归属。希望足下急速再度进兵，收<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>，据守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">敖仓</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">粟</span>，塞住<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">成皋</span>的险要，堵住<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大行</span>的道路，封锁<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蜚狐</span>的口子，守住<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">白马</span>的渡口，以此向<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>显示形势和控制之势，那么<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>就知道归向哪里了。如今<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>已平定，只有<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>未攻下。如今<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田广</span>据<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千里</span>之<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田间</span>率<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十万之众</span>，驻军于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">历城</span>，诸<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">田</span>宗族强盛，背靠大海、凭借<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济水</span>为阻，南邻<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，人多善变诈，足下即使派<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数十万</span>军队，也不能在短期内<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>之。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>请求奉明诏去说服<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">齐王</span>，让<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，做东方的藩属。\" 皇上说：\"好。\""
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "于是听从他的计谋，又守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">敖仓</span>，而派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>游说<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">齐王</span>说：\"大王知道<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的归属吗？\" 王说：\"不知道。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>说：\"大王知道<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的归属，那么<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国可以保有；如果不知<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的归属，那么<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国就难以保全了。\" <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">齐王</span>说：\"<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>归向哪里？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>说：\"归向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>。\" <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">齐王</span>说：\"先生为什么这么说？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项王</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">戮</span>力西面<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，约定先入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>的称王。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>先入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项王</span>违约不给他而让他王<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汉中</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项王</span>迁放<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">义帝</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>听说后，起<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>之兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">三秦</span>，出关而问<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">义帝</span>所在，收<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>之兵，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>之后。攻下城邑就封给将领为侯，得到财物就分给<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒，与<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>同利，豪杰贤才都乐于为他所用。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>之兵四面而至，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">粟</span>米并<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">船</span>而下。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项王</span>有背约之名，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">义帝</span>的罪过；对别人的功劳无所记载，对别人的罪过却无所遗忘；<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>胜而不赏功，攻城而不封爵；不是<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">项氏</span>族人就不能用事；替人刻了<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">印</span>，摸到磨损都舍不得颁授；<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>城获得财物，积着不能赏：<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>背叛他，贤才怨恨他，没有人为他所用。所以<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>归于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>，是可以坐着谋划就能得到的。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>发兵，平定<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">三秦</span>；渡过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西河</span>之外，接收<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上党</span>之兵；下<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">井陉</span>，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成安君</span>；<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">北魏</span>，攻取三十二城：这是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蚩尤</span>之兵，不是人力，是天之福助。如今已据<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">敖仓</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">粟</span>，塞住<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">成皋</span>的险要，守住<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">白马</span>的渡口，堵住<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大行</span>的山坡，封锁<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蜚狐</span>的口子，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>后归服的就先灭亡。大王赶快先归附<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">社稷</span>可以保全；不归附<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>，危亡立刻到来。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田广</span>认为对，就听从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">罢</span>去<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">历下</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">兵守</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>备，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>日日纵情饮<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">酒</span>。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">淮阴侯（韩信）</span>听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>凭借车轼而下<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">七十馀城</span>，就连夜率兵渡过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平原</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">袭</span>击<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">齐王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田广</span>听说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>兵来到，以为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>出卖了自己，就说：\"你能让<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>军停止进攻，我就让你活；否则，我就要烹你！\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>说：\"举大事不拘细节，盛德不辞让。你老子不替你再改口！\" <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">齐王</span>于是烹了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>，带兵东逃。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十二年</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">曲周侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦商</span>以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>身份率兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黥布</span>有功。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>推举<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">功臣</span>，思念<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦食其</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦食其</span>的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：郦疥\">疥（郦疥）</span>多次率兵作战，功劳不当封侯，皇上因其父之故，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：郦疥\">疥（郦疥）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">高梁侯</span>。后来改<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">食</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武遂</span>，传了三代。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元狩元年</span>中，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">武遂侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：郦平\">平（郦平）</span>因诈传诏命向<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">衡山王</span>索<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">百斤金</span>，应当<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">弃市</span>，病死，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">国除</span>。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆贾</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>人。以客卿身份跟从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>平定<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，以有口才闻名，是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">辩士</span>，居于皇帝左右，常出使<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>时，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>初定，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尉他</span>平定<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>，因而称王。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆贾</span>赐给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尉他</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">印</span>封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">南越王</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>到后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尉他</span>椎髻箕坐地接见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>于是上前劝说他说：\"足下是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>人，亲戚兄弟的坟墓在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">真定</span>。如今足下违反天性，丢弃<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">冠带</span>，想以区区<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>地与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>抗衡为敌国，祸将及身。况且<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>失其政，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>豪杰并起，只有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>先入关，据<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>背约，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">西楚霸王</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>都归属他，可谓至强。然而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">巴</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span>起兵，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">鞭</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">笞</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，劫略<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，于是<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>灭了他。五年之间，海内平定，这不是人力，是上天所建立。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>听说<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君王</span>王<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>，不助<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>暴逆，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">将相</span>想调兵来<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>王，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>怜悯<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>新近劳苦，所以暂且让他们休息，派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>授<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君王</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">印</span>，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">剖符</span>通使。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君王</span>应当郊迎，面北称<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>，却想以新造未稳的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国，在此倔强抵抗。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝若真听闻此事，挖烧王祖先坟墓，夷灭宗族，派一个偏将率<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十万众</span>临<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>，那么<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>人会<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>王降<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，就像翻手一样容易。\""
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尉他</span>惊而起身端坐，向<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>道歉说：\"在<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">蛮夷</span>中久居，很失<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">礼义</span>了。\" 因此问<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>说：\"我与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧何</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹参</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩信</span>比谁更贤？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>说：\"大王似乎更贤。\" 又问：\"我与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span>比谁更贤？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span>起兵于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">丰</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>，讨伐暴<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>灭强<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，为<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>兴利除害，继<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">五帝</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">三王</span>的大业，统理<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>之人以亿计，地方<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万里</span>，居<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的膏腴之地，人众<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车轝</span>，万物殷富，政出自<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一家</span>，从<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">天地</span>开辟以来从未有过。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">今王</span>部众不过<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数十万</span>，都是<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">蛮夷</span>，崎岖于山海之间，就像<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>的一个郡，大王怎能与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>相比！\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尉他</span>大笑说：\"我不是在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>起兵，所以在此为王。假使我住在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>，何以不如<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>？\" 于是十分喜爱<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>，留他一起饮酒<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数月（时长）</span>。又说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>中没有人可与谈话，等先生来，令我每天听到过去未曾听到的。\" 赐给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">橐</span>中所装价值<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">千金</span>的礼物，另外送的也有<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">千金</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>终于<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">拜</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尉他</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">南越王</span>，让他称<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>尊奉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>约。回朝禀报，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>大喜，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">拜</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陆贾\">贾（陆贾）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太中大夫</span>。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>常常在皇上面前称述<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：诗\">诗经（诗）</span><span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：书\">尚书（书）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>骂他说：\"你老子是在<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>上得来的，哪里用得着<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：诗\">诗经（诗）</span><span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：书\">尚书（书）</span>！\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>说：\"在<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>上得来的，难道可以在<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>上治理吗？况且<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周武王\">武（周武王）</span>逆<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>而以顺守之，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周文王\">文（周文王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周武王\">武（周武王）</span>并用文武之道，这是长久之术。从前<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夫差</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">智伯</span>极用武力而亡；<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>任用<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">刑法</span>不变，终被<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">赵氏</span>所灭。假使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>已吞并<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，施行<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">仁义</span>，效法前代圣贤，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>怎能得到这<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>不悦而面有惭色，于是对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>说：\"试为我著述<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>所以失<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>、我所以得<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的原因是什么，以及古代成<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">之国</span>。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>于是大略叙述存亡的征兆，共著十二篇。每奏一篇，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>无不称善，左右呼万岁，称其书为\"<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">新语</span>\"。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝惠帝</span>时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕太后</span>专权用事，想封诸<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">吕</span>为王，畏惧有口才的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>自己估量不能与之争，就称病免官居家。因<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">好畤</span>的田地好，可以安家。他有五个儿子，就拿出出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>所得<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">橐</span>中装的卖出<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">千金</span>，分给儿子们，每人二百<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>，令他们置办产业。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>常坐着安<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">驷马</span>，随从歌舞鼓<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">琴</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">瑟</span>的侍者<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十人</span>，宝<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>值<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百金</span>，对儿子们说：\"与你们约定：我经过你家，你家就供应我这些人马酒食，极尽欢娱，十日后换一家。我死在谁家，谁就得到<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">宝剑</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车骑</span>侍从。一年中还要往来拜访其他客人，大概不过两三次，<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">数见不鲜</span>，不要久劳你们了。\""
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕太后</span>时，封诸<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">吕</span>为王，诸<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">吕</span>擅权，想劫持<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">少主</span>，危及<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">刘氏</span>。 <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">右丞相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>为此忧虑，力不能争，担心祸及自身，常独自静处深思。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>前去拜访，径直入座，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈丞相</span>正在深思，没有及时见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>说：\"何以深思至此？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>说：\"先生猜我在想什么？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>说：\"足下位居<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">上相</span>，食<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三万户</span>侯，可谓富贵极致无欲了。然而有忧念，不过是担心诸<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">吕</span>、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">少主</span>罢了。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>说：\"是。怎么办？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>说：\"<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>安定，注意相；<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>危难，注意将。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">将相</span>和调，则<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人都愿依附；<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人都愿依附，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>即使有变，权力就不分散。为<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">社稷</span>计，就在两<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>掌握之中。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>常想对<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">绛侯</span>说，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">绛侯</span>与我戏谈，轻视我的话。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>何不与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span>交好，深相结交？\" 又为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>筹划对付<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">吕氏</span>的几件事。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>采用他的计策，就以<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">五百金</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">绛侯</span>祝寿，准备了丰盛的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">乐</span>饮；<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span>也照样回报。 两人深相结交，<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">吕氏</span>之谋也就日益衰减。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>又送给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>奴婢<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百人</span>，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车马</span>五十乘，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">钱五百万</span>，作为饮<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">食</span>费用。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>以此游于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>廷<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公卿</span>之间，名声甚大。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "到<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>诸<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">吕</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文帝</span>时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>颇有功劳。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文帝</span>即位后，想派人出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈丞相</span>等便推荐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太中大夫</span>，前往出使<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尉他</span>，令<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尉他</span>去掉<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">黄屋</span>、不再<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">称制</span>，令他比同<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，都合<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">如意</span>旨。这些话记在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>传中。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>最终以寿终。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">朱建</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>人。过去曾做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">淮南王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黥布</span>的相，有罪而去，后又事奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黥布</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>想反叛时，问<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>反对，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>不听而听从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">梁父侯</span>，于是反叛。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>已<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span>，听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>曾谏而不预谋反，得以免<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>。这些话记在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黥布</span>传中。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>为人善辩有口才，清廉刚直，家在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>。行事不苟合，以义不取悦于人。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辟阳侯</span>行为不正，却得宠于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕太后</span>。当时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辟阳侯</span>想结交<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>不肯相见。等到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>的母亲去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>一向与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>交好，前去吊唁。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>家贫，没有发丧，正在借贷操办丧服器具，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>先发丧。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>前去见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辟阳侯</span>，贺道：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>的母亲去世了。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辟阳侯</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>的母亲死了，怎么向我道贺呢？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆贾</span>说：\"前些日<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>侯想结交<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>守义不肯结交<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>，是因为母亲的缘故。如今他母亲去世，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>如果真能厚赠送丧，那他就会为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>去死。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辟阳侯</span>于是奉送<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">百金</span>前去赠葬。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贵人</span>因<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辟阳侯</span>的缘故，前去赠葬的共有<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">五百金</span>。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辟阳侯</span>得宠于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕太后</span>，有人在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝惠帝</span>面前诋毁<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辟阳侯</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝惠帝</span>大怒，交给法吏审讯，想<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕太后</span>惭愧，不便说情。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>多痛恨<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辟阳侯</span>的行为，想就此<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辟阳侯</span>急迫，派人想求见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>推辞说：\"狱事紧急，不敢见<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>。\" 于是求见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孝惠帝\">孝惠（孝惠帝）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">幸臣</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">闳籍孺</span>，劝他说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>得宠于皇帝，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>无人不知。如今<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辟阳侯</span>得宠于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>而被下狱，道路上都说<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>进了谗言，想<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>他。今日<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辟阳侯</span>被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>，明日<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>含怒，也会<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>。何不袒露上身为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辟阳侯</span>向<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">帝</span>说情？<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">帝</span>若听<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>之言放出<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辟阳侯</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>会大喜。两主共同宠幸<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>的富贵就更加倍了。\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">闳籍孺</span>大惧，听从他的计策，对<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">帝</span>说了，果然放出<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辟阳侯</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辟阳侯</span>被囚时，想见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>不肯见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辟阳侯</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辟阳侯</span>以为他背叛了自己，大怒。等到成功救出他时，才大为吃惊。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕太后</span>崩，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>诸<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">吕</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辟阳侯</span>与诸<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">吕</span>关系极深，却最终没被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>。计划所以能保全他的，都是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>的功劳。"
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文帝</span>时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">淮南厉王</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辟阳侯</span>，是因诸<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">吕</span>的缘故。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">辟阳侯</span>的门客<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>为他出谋划策，派官吏捕捉要治罪。 听说官吏到家门口，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>想<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">自杀</span>。 诸子及官吏都说：\"事情尚未可知，何必早早<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">自杀</span>？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>说：\"我死祸就断绝，不连累到你们。\" 于是自刎。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文帝</span>听说后为他惋惜，说：\"我无意<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>他。\" 就召他的儿子，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">拜</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中大夫</span>。 出使<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>无<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼</span>，他就骂<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>，于是死在<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>中。"
    },
    "20": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "起初，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>率兵经过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈留</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>到军门前求见说：\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">高阳</span>贱<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦食其</span>，私下听闻<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>风餐露宿，率兵助<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>讨伐不义，特此敬慰随从，希望得到拜见，口述<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>便利之事。\" 使者入内通报，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>正在洗脚，问使者说：\"是什么样的人？\" 使者回答说：\"状貌像大儒，穿<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">儒衣</span>，戴<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">侧注</span>冠。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>说：\"替我谢绝他，就说我正以<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>为事，没空闲见儒人。\" 使者出来谢绝说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>敬谢先生，正以<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>为事，没空闲见儒人。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>瞪眼按<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>叱使者说：\"滚！再进去告诉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>，我是<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">高阳酒徒</span>，不是儒人。\" 使者恐惧掉了谒帖，跪下拾起，回身就跑，又入内禀报说：\"那客人，是<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>壮<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>，斥骂<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>恐惧，以致掉了谒帖。他说'滚！再入内告诉，你老子是<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">高阳酒徒</span>'。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>急忙擦脚拄<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">矛</span>说：\"请客人进来！\""
    },
    "21": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>入内，对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>作揖说：\"足下甚苦，风尘仆仆、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">冠</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">衣</span>尽露，率兵助<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>讨不义，你怎么不自爱呢？<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>原以求见议事，你却说'我正以<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>为事，没空见儒人'。足下想兴<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>大事而成<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>大功，却以外表取人，恐怕要失去<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>有能的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人。况且我估计足下的智谋不如我，勇力也不如我。若欲成就<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>事业而不愿相见，我私下以为足下失策。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>谢罪说：\"刚才听人描述先生的容貌，如今已见到先生的心意了。\" 于是延请他入座，问他如何<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>说：\"足下想成大功，不如留驻<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈留</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈留</span>，是<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的要冲，兵家必争之地，积<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">粟</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数千万石</span>，城防坚固。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>一向与其令交好，愿为足下去游说他。他若不听<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>请为足下<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了他，然后攻下<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈留</span>。足下统率<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈留</span>的众人，据守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈留</span>的城池，而取用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：郦食其\">食其（郦食其）</span>积储的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">粟</span>米，招集<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>之从兵；从兵既成，足下就可横行<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，没人能伤害足下了。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>说：\"敬闻命令。\""
    },
    "22": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>连夜去见<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈留</span>令，游说他说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝无道，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>背叛它，如今足下与<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>合纵则可以成大功。如今独自为亡<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>环城坚守，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>私下为足下担忧。\" <span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈留</span>令说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>极严，不可以妄言，妄言之人灭族，我不能响应。先生教导<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>的，不合<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>的意，愿先生不要再说了。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>留宿，到<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">夜半</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>下<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈留</span>令的头，翻越城墙下来回报<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>率兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>城，把<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">县令</span>的头悬在长<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">竿</span>上给城上人看，说：\"快投降，你们的县令头已被砍下！今后投降晚的必先被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>！\" 于是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈留</span>人见县令已死，就相率投降<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈留</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南城</span>门上安营，取用其武库的兵器，食用积储的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">粟</span>米，往来出入三月，从军的以<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万数</span>，于是入关<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。"
    },
    "23": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：世上传<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>的书，多说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>已攻下<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">三秦</span>，东<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项籍（项羽）</span>而领兵在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">巩洛</span>之间，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>穿<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">儒衣</span>前去游说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>。这不是事实。自<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>未入关之前，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>分别而到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">高阳</span>时，就已得到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span>兄弟。我读<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆生</span>的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">新语</span>十二篇，确是当世的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">辩士</span>。至于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>的儿子与我交好，所以得以详细论述他们的事迹。"
    },
    "24": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：郦食其\">广野（郦食其）</span>器量大度，起初戴<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">侧注</span>。 到军门前长揖，受沛公器重礼遇。 说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">历下</span>，见<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">鼎</span>无所畏惧。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆贾</span>出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>地，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：尉他\">尉佗（尉他）</span>被其震慑。 劝说国家安定，著书令主省悟。"
    }
  }
}